; Import into Cloudflare: DNS → Records → Import and Export → Import DNS records
; neelmind.com — website + Hostinger Mail
; Verify DKIM value against hPanel export before importing.
; Proxy: set A/CNAME to DNS only (grey cloud); never proxy MX.

@       300 IN A     187.127.189.114
www     300 IN CNAME neelmind.com.
@       300 IN MX    5 mx1.hostinger.com.
@       300 IN MX    10 mx2.hostinger.com.
@       300 IN TXT   "v=spf1 include:_spf.mail.hostinger.com ~all"
_dmarc  300 IN TXT   "v=DMARC1; p=none"
hostingermail-a._domainkey 300 IN TXT "v=DKIM1;k=rsa;"
